<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM1.3.2">
<l>mutuku paṟṟik kaitta lattāl muṉṉo rukōlūṉṟi</l>
<l>vitirvi tirttuk kaṇcu ḻaṉṟu mēṟki ḷaikoṇṭirumi</l>
<l>ituveṉ ṉappar mūtta vāṟeṉ ṟiḷaiya varēcāmuṉ</l>
<l>matuvuṇ vaṇṭu paṇkaḷ pāṭum vatari vaṇaṅkutumē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Catching at [my] back with the palm of [my] hand,</l>
<l rend="indent">steadying in front with a staff,</l>
<l>Forcefully trembling, rolling [my] eyes, coughing with a rattle</l>
<l rend="indent">in [my] upper [chest],</l>
<l>Before young girls can scorn [me], saying, “What is this?</l>
<l rend="indent">How ancient [this] man is!”</l>
<l>We will worship at Badarī where bees that suck nectar sing melodies.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
